org.xlattice.corexml.om

Class Holder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xlattice.corexml.om.Node
      • org.xlattice.corexml.om.Holder
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Document, Element

    public abstract class Holder
extends Node
    A Holder is something which can have children and namespaces, so a Document or an Element.
    Author:
    Jim Dixon
